* '''2005,''' Stuart MacBride, ''Cold Granite'' [http://books.google.com/books?ie=UTF-8&hl=en&id=W-rOBVj-V8EC&pg=PA106&lpg=PA106&sig=cJqRBSzOJDxELHhg9uGVxsJgJrs]
